summary:
I had a theory about why Taylor released her first single of ts7 on 4.26. 
Turn ME! upside down and it goes to 13W, which is 13...
body:
I had a theory about why Taylor released her first single of ts7 on 4.26.

Turn ME! upside down and it goes to 13W, which is 13 weeks. It’s pretty obvious on the thumbnail of lyric video.

13 weeks = 2.992 months.

2.992 * 365 / 10 = 109.

4.26 + 109 days = 8.13, another wax seal on calendar .

And she always release her lead single in August, from “mine” to “look what you made me do”.

8*13 also equals to 4*26. So I suppose it’s a keeping with tradition.
